# Abstract: Environmental pollution by toxic compounds affects various species of living organisms
column2: their life cycles and symbiotic relationships. This study investigated the host-parasite relationship between Tenebrio molitor Linnaeus

We measured the body weight and survival rate of T. molitor and the number of G. steini in them to assess the impact of the tested organic compounds on the host-parasite relationship. For all the compounds studied
